					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->ROCHESTER, Minn. — For 100 years, Mayo Clinic Proceedings has helped shape the course of modern medicine — publishing discoveries that move from the page to the bedside and improve care for patients around the world. As the journal approaches its centennial in April 2026, Mayo Clinic is marking the milestone with events, exhibitions and […]<p></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/a-century-of-discovery-mayo-clinic-proceedings-marks-100-years-of-advancing-medical-research-education-and-practice/">A century of discovery: Mayo Clinic Proceedings marks 100 years of advancing medical research, education and practice</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
